lines:
Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Longstop is home of gobbieflock! Craftybuilt by gobbiehands!
Then flighty-beast comes and claims Longstop as lair. Brayflox cannot abide─Brayflox and gobbieflock backtake with uplander hand-lending!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Goodly uplander is talentful plansmaker! Will trade tongueflaps with Wheiskaet so all know of hand-lending!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Mighty rockman no match for wily uplander and clever fighty-think! Brayflox happytoasts fall of rockman!

obj.n: ブレイフロクスの珍チーズ
